    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved\u2014runs like a dream and is ready to hit the road with a new owner! It\u2019s the perfect reliable ride for someone who wants quality without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see how smooth it feels. Drop me a message if you're interested!",
      "price": 33500.0,
