    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and consistently maintained so it's ready to hit the road. Everything runs smoothly, and it\u2019s just looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated as much as I have. It's been perfect for my daily commutes and weekend trips. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all; I'm super happy to chat and give you all the details!",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
