      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offered is a 2004 BMW M3 Coupe featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This driver-focused example utilizes a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical mechanical addressals include a reinforced rear subframe and a top-end refresh to ensure the 8,000 RPM redline remains accessible. The chassis retains its signature balance with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering feedback. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust with crisp gear engagement and linear power delivery across the entire rev range.",
